          Shape Your Future with <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563EB 0%, #14B8A6 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Premium Education</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted mb-4" style="line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.15rem; color: #475569;">
          Unlock boundless career pathways, state-of-the-art laboratory access, and personalized mentorship. Fill out our simple inquiry form to schedule a one-on-one consultation with our dedicated academic counsellors today.
        </p>
        
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-5">
          <a href="<%= student ? '/inquiry' : '/student/login' %>" class="btn btn-primary-blue px-4 py-3" style="font-size: 1rem; border-radius: 8px;"><i class="bi bi-pencil-square me-2"></i>Apply Now</a>
          <a href="#programs" class="btn btn-outline-blue px-4 py-3" style="font-size: 1rem; border-radius: 8px;"><i class="bi bi-book-half me-2"></i>Explore Programs</a>
